{
  "texts": [
    "However, the pre-processing step used to eliminate the noise and dark background limits the usage of this model in a more generic context and makes the comparison with other studies in the literature misleading due to the difference in the test dataset.",
    "Recently, Malik et al.",
    "[44] used a subset of 16984 elbow X-ray radiographs from the MURA dataset to test the model's performance to classify elbow abnormalities.",
    "First, they proposed adding a pre-processing step to convert images to RGB colour space.",
    "Then, the Xception and DarkNetwork-53 architectures were used to extract deep features."
  ]
}